<p>$$2022^{2022} \\equiv 2^{2022} \\equiv 2^{2020} \\cdot 2^{2} \\equiv\\left(2^{4}\\right)^{505} \\cdot 4 \\equiv 6 \\cdot 4 \\equiv 4 \\pmod {10}.$$ </p>
